edu.xtec.jclic.automation

Class AutoContentProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.xtec.jclic.automation.AutoContentProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Editable, Domable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Arith, TagReplace

    public abstract class AutoContentProvider
extends Object
implements Domable, Editable
    This abstract class is the base for all the classes that provide contents to JClic activities, usually based on random values. Activities linked to a AutoContentProvider object rely on it to build its contents on every start.
    Version:
    13.09.10
    Author:
    Francesc Busquets (fbusquets@xtec.cat)
